Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.51,0:01:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希緒弗斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.52,0:01:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 這傢伙就是希緒弗斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.05,0:01:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙的靈魂就由我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.00,0:01:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.80,0:02:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見嘍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.61,0:02:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅典娜大人 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.08,0:02:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您果然在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.94,0:02:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白禮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.65,0:02:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾爾熙德的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.26,0:02:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能把希緒弗斯的靈魂帶回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.36,0:02:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是個會貫徹自我信念的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.32,0:02:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算受到四神的威脅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.08,0:02:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也一定能克服它 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.30,0:02:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然不惜出動四神也要來對付無法動彈的希緒弗斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.73,0:02:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.91,0:02:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是因為看的到動作 才能找到破綻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.77,0:02:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓你逃脫的 修普諾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.20,0:03:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.85,0:03:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.13,0:03:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砍飛的會是我的右臂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.59,0:03:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連一聲慘叫都沒麼 艾爾熙德
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.02,0:03:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.60,0:03:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如何
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.87,0:03:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用自己的手臂 品味自己引以為豪的劍術
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.09,0:03:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的手臂…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.23,0:03:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.09,0:03:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把空間扭曲了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.19,0:03:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你從前方放出的劍壓 被我移到了你的側面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.85,0:04:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小菜一碟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.01,0:04:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩弄也要適可而止 伊刻羅斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.13,0:04:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點結果了他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.76,0:04:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這隻手臂我就收下了哦 聖鬥士先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.29,0:04:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真是獵奇啊 幻塔索斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.85,0:04:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為就失去一條手臂 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.22,0:04:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖鬥士就會放棄嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.15,0:05:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連黃金聖鬥士也不過如此嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.59,0:05:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊刻羅斯 幻塔索斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.48,0:05:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續任務吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.18,0:05:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是抓捕天馬座
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.40,0:05:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧涅伊洛斯喲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.39,0:05:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去把天馬星座抓來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.60,0:05:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是靈魂 把肉體也一起丟入夢界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.58,0:05:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是說把肉體也？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.77,0:05:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說他只是青銅聖鬥士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.85,0:05:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是和冥王哈迪斯大人有切不斷的因緣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.23,0:05:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分危險
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.90,0:05:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須避免一些人的干擾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.75,0:05:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.43,0:05:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓他無法再次轉生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.87,0:05:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而將他隔離在夢界麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.75,0:05:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓捕青銅的天馬座 簡直太小兒科了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.99,0:05:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就去好好歡迎歡迎他們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.69,0:05:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.99,0:05:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把天馬座連同肉體 帶往夢界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.18,0:05:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢界？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.69,0:06:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 切希爾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.47,0:06:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈迪斯大人現在正在夢界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.93,0:06:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳說曾經連宙斯都被囚禁的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.63,0:06:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何人都無法侵入的神靈之魂的沉睡之地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.31,0:06:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.03,0:06:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡的話 就能不被任何人干擾的完成lost canvas了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.39,0:06:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣 他就能忘卻可憎的人類之心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.25,0:06:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淨化靈魂了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.83,0:06:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.76,0:06:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我心中的騷動無法平息
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.39,0:06:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霧好濃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.58,0:06:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是沒時間了 趕路要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.99,0:06:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈迪斯城已經很近了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.31,0:07:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞倫 等著我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.75,0:07:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.83,0:07:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.66,0:07:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這片樹林…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.13,0:07:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有印象…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.08,0:07:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霧比剛才更重了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.08,0:07:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 這樣前面就看不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.90,0:07:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 天馬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.32,0:07:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.79,0:07:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 跟丟了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.58,0:07:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙 樣子有點怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.54,0:07:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.98,0:08:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.58,0:08:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城鎮…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城鎮不是已經被毀了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.75,0:08:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明已經毀滅的我的故鄉…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.93,0:08:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是敵人製造的幻象嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.35,0:08:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說 至今經歷的事才是夢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.75,0:08:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬？！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.64,0:08:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 這副模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.34,0:08:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渾身都是泥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.63,0:09:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又打架了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.03,0:09:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次是和誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.40,0:09:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.29,0:09:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成了薩沙的 雅典娜的聖鬥士
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.87,0:09:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞倫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.63,0:09:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是毀滅了城鎮的冥王哈迪斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.69,0:09:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.72,0:09:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在說的話和現實脫軌了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.11,0:09:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 你在說你的夢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.96,0:09:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 夢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.61,0:09:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 是啊 就是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.47,0:09:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞倫哥哥怎麼可能是哈迪斯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.46,0:09:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是夢…嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.36,0:09:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩個人是神明
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.17,0:09:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互相廝殺什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.90,0:09:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 天馬 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.78,0:09:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是噩夢而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.53,0:09:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 天空如此的蔚藍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.90,0:09:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和往常一樣的今日
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.60,0:09:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們三個人的日子 是永恆的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.34,0:10:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永恆…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.13,0:10:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 永恆…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.92,0:10:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是夢啊 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.67,0:10:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣天馬座的靈魂就墜入夢界了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.61,0:10:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊刻羅斯喲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.75,0:10:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墨菲斯回到自己該待的地方了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.68,0:10:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 回到他的轄區 墨菲亞去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.26,0:10:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墨菲亞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.96,0:10:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算在夢界也是帝王和英雄的靈魂沉睡 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.18,0:10:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡庸的靈魂無法進入的場所
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.96,0:10:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感到榮幸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.36,0:10:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也將被囚禁在此 永遠的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.87,0:11:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連肉體都通過這扇門的人 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.91,0:11:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去曾有過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.32,0:11:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.91,0:11:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不記得有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.59,0:11:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個笨蛋 跑哪去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.85,0:11:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耶人 小心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.83,0:11:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.00,0:11:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.16,0:11:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我還以為會是怎樣的聖鬥士呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.16,0:11:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是個可愛的男孩兒～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.93,0:11:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.28,0:12:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女 女人？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.87,0:12:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冥鬥士嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.10,0:12:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.92,0:12:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的小宇宙遠遠超過冥鬥士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.28,0:12:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.58,0:12:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.41,0:12:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓葉！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.09,0:12:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣可不行哦 女孩子如此粗魯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.57,0:12:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你怎麼可能贏呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.39,0:12:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面對神！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.05,0:12:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.79,0:12:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是夢四神之一 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.18,0:12:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻塔索斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.15,0:12:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怖幻想曲（Grim phantasy）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.12,0:12:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.78,0:12:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來帶你們去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.16,0:12:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們所期望的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.81,0:12:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.10,0:12:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法動彈…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.53,0:13:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒有挑戰性呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.20,0:13:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安心睡吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.10,0:13:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使你們的肉身腐爛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.03,0:13:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會讓你們的心幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.70,0:13:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們做個好夢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.34,0:14:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個就沉醉在美好的夢境裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.42,0:14:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.18,0:14:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空間出現了龜裂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.88,0:14:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.08,0:14:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟能從現實入侵這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.75,0:14:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙 不是已經被伊刻羅斯收拾了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.43,0:15:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何會在此處
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.22,0:15:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你拿著的一部分…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.80,0:15:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃金聖衣在呼喚我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.14,0:15:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.93,0:15:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用與黃金聖衣的共鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.87,0:15:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來到了這夢界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.51,0:15:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以那時…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.60,0:15:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此輕易地被幹掉…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.62,0:15:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自認為讓身為神明的我上鉤了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.26,0:15:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使有夢界牆壁的隔閡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.72,0:15:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖衣的聲音依然不止
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.94,0:15:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刃仍在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.39,0:15:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,召喚我來奪 站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.73,0:15:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個讓人歡樂的黃金聖鬥士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.34,0:15:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.84,0:15:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是夢界中掌管人類夢想的場所 幻想曲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.66,0:15:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼夢想都能成真哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.48,0:15:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擺出這麼嚴肅的表情嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.21,0:15:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起來享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.42,0:16:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.64,0:16:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有想見的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.16,0:16:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都會如你所願哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.51,0:16:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怖幻想曲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.87,0:16:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇到你了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.01,0:16:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這空間中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.96,0:16:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說小宇宙 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.11,0:16:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連身體的自由也可以奪走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.48,0:16:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 讓我來幫你實現 你未能實現的夢想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.17,0:16:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那張撲克臉背後
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.62,0:16:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隱藏著什麼欲望呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.16,0:16:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.52,0:16:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.26,0:17:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.17,0:17:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.60,0:17:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是讓自己的拳頭進化為終極之刃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.23,0:17:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外 我別無所求
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.66,0:17:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道？！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.75,0:17:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在夢中都要貫徹自身的道路？！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.51,0:18:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你偽裝的外皮被剝掉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.24,0:18:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區區一介骯髒人類…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.00,0:18:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟毀了本神的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.27,0:18:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美貌！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.02,0:18:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饒不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.44,0:18:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.85,0:18:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.08,0:18:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就用恐怖幻想曲 把你的肉體一起毀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.62,0:18:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刃仍在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.67,0:18:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,召喚我來奪 站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.87,0:18:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伴隨著進一步的鋒利！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.24,0:19:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還剩下三神
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.82,0:19:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.19,0:19:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在哪見過
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.61,0:19:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是夢境
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.80,0:20:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是轉動起我們三人命運齒輪的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.12,0:20:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希緒弗斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.16,0:20:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.82,0:20:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.84,0:20:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五年前…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.63,0:20:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希緒弗斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.80,0:20:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然這不是夢境
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.20,0:20:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會是夢呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.24,0:20:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.95,0:20:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬座聖鬥士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.61,0:20:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬座的夢境似乎有什麼異變
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.86,0:20:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 剛聽到了幻塔索斯慘叫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.06,0:20:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且感受到了山羊座的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.13,0:20:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這其中必定有什麼關聯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.67,0:20:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到這夢界中竟會發生動搖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.06,0:20:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.36,0:20:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便從夢中蘇醒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.35,0:21:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬座仍然身在墨菲亞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.12,0:21:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給墨菲斯 應該不會有什麼問題
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.64,0:21:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山羊座就由我來料理
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.30,0:21:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說到底 沒給他致命一擊的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.16,0:21:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個男人…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.90,0:21:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了手臂 還能抑制住慘叫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.85,0:21:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的興趣來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.91,0:21:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的尊嚴要到什麼程度才會被挫敗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.64,0:21:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我掌管的恐怖症中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.76,0:21:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能忍耐到什麼程度
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.95,0:21:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.43,0:21:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是你 想必可以輕鬆解決吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.69,0:21:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊刻羅斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.13,0:21:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按住真央點止血
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.53,0:21:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是拖延時間嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.26,0:21:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚎叫聲？！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.71,0:22:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到你竟然踏入夢界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.59,0:22:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來剁你一隻手臂還不夠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.59,0:22:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾爾熙德
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.56,0:22:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻夢 伊刻羅斯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.08,0:22:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找你很久了…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.98,0:24:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修普諾斯大人 天馬好像覺察到了異變
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.70,0:24:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過請大人無需掛心
